		\midrule
		TRIBE           & 7.80 & 22.59 & 0.138   \\
		Hierarchical    & 7.57 & 24.16 & 0.133   \\
		Correlated      & 7.49 & 25.76 & 0.134   \\
		Sparse          & 8.12 & 19.27 & 0.165   \\
		Curved Manifold & 7.74 & 23.50 & 0.134   \\
		\bottomrule
	\end{tabular}
\end{table}

Figure \ref{fig:parameter_space} shows the parameter space representation of the five systems, illustrating their positions in the 3D space defined by ($A$, $k_0$, $\beta$).

